  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to access the efficacy and safety of Mizoribine 150mg qid and
      50mg tid in active rheumatoid arthritis patients unsuccessfully treated with
      disease-modifying antirheumatic drug.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      1. EULAR Response after 24weeks of treatment

        2. EULAR Response after 12weeks of treatment

        3. DAS28 value change

        4. KHAQ-20 value change
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
